<scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
<head>Scope and Content
</head>
<p>This is a collection of four photographs of Charlottesville locations by an unidentified photographer. They include the First Methodist Church on Jefferson Street, the statue in front of St. Thomas Aquinas Church, the University of Virginia Rotunda, and three unidentified children near Central Plaza on the Downtown Mall.
</p>
</scopecontent>

